<p class="has-line-data" data-line-start="89" data-line-end="90">You can also run the following command to list installed modules only:</p>
<pre><code class="html">php -m
</code></pre>
<ol start="10">
<li class="has-line-data" data-line-start="95" data-line-end="97">Start &amp; Configure MariaDB</li>
</ol>
<pre><code class="html">systemctl start mariadb.service
systemctl status mariadb
</code></pre>
